218
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,360
Apa pun,

219
00:13:03,810 --> 00:13:05,720
sekurang-kurangnya Putera Jin ambil tindakan.

220
00:13:06,450 --> 00:13:07,570
Tak seperti Ji Mo.

221
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:09,760
