222
00:13:13,570 --> 00:13:14,210
Apa?

223
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:16,360
Kamu nak melamar Qiao Manman?

224
00:13:16,760 --> 00:13:18,050
Bukankah kamu berdua baru saja berkahwin?

225
00:13:18,288 --> 00:13:20,644
Yang di kediaman Putera Jin itu tak dikira.

226
00:13:20,810 --> 00:13:22,720
Aku belum rasmi berkahwin dengan Manman.

227
00:13:23,530 --> 00:13:26,000
Dan Encik Qiao belum suruh aku tukar cara panggil dia.

228
00:13:26,810 --> 00:13:27,840
Aku perlu jelaskan kedudukan aku

229
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,240
dalam Persatuan Segalanya.

230
00:13:33,170 --> 00:13:34,170
